{"tid":538811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"約定俗成 -「左」同「o左」","createTime":"2018-01-24T03:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T04:33:23.000Z","uid":143505,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6de4c78d13370717fd238e8cd43eb7dd933a96","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:35:36.000Z","msg":"直接舉兩個例子<br />\n跌打個跌係應該跌親個跌<br />\n但當你聽到有人讀做鐵打嘅時候<br />\n你唔會刻意糾正佢<br />\n又或者<br />\n彌字應該讀做微而唔係尼<br />\n但當你聽到有人讀做尼敦道嘅時候<br />\n你亦都唔會刻意糾正佢<br />\n因為呢啲嘅「錯誤」大家都有共識<br />\n同「左」「o左」(手機打唔到)一樣<br />\n不過「吾系甘牙」一直以嚟都被認為應該打做「唔係咁呀」<br />\n所以可以話係兩個唔同嘅情況<br />\n不過你要捉 當然可以捉<br />\n只不過真係好無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950aa0a6bd605a5ed79b5c70466f1f1df713574e","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64103329e4c8135d30fd8aedb274a7bf1a4c3e75","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"希望大家少啲鬧交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6babddc0cf8126fe8c6a0db1739000aa08afbbc","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"5af71d55bf524d7cb44706e6e36c3954677e0b82","tid":538811,"uid":127292,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cd3a3ab4ec18f8b4cf2557a3d0b373a227e7c32","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5af71d55bf524d7cb44706e6e36c3954677e0b82","tid":538811,"uid":127292,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"但至少我覺得捉左係有d無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fc29ef2668132902da70566920f7145de45574","tid":538811,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"彌係一字多音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可讀微可讀尼<br />\n唔可以話尼唔係其中正確讀法，而依家普及黎講都係聽尼音多過微音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93586336b5b4e24ef22952d549cc5d75aa57120f","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88fc29ef2668132902da70566920f7145de45574","tid":538811,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"彌係一字多音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可讀微可讀尼<br />\n唔可以話尼唔係其中正確讀法，而依家普及黎講都係聽尼音多過微音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"其實多人讀尼都唔代表係正音<br />\n只不過大家都有共識接受呢個讀音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7faa57fa3bc257ffb15ae21dc6cbfdbed71292ea","tid":538811,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"同埋彌敦道讀尼敦係因為音譯nathan，呢個係外國傳音<br />\n咁你話讀尼敦近啲定微敦近呢<br />\n仲話你讀微敦唔會糾正人地尼敦<br />\n正常應該係人地讀尼敦去糾正你先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f36d9037994a0749dc30edcf4ad2e781cfb399","tid":538811,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔肯用正字咪唔會畀人捉囉！明明錯係自己，人地屌正你又忠言逆耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n忠你老母"},{"pid":"5e751d81dead3e0f30a95bc5a0d7c7733928ac5a","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7faa57fa3bc257ffb15ae21dc6cbfdbed71292ea","tid":538811,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"同埋彌敦道讀尼敦係因為音譯nathan，呢個係外國傳音<br />\n咁你話讀尼敦近啲定微敦近呢<br />\n仲話你讀微敦唔會糾正人地尼敦<br />\n正常應該係人地讀尼敦去糾正你先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"咁如果係音譯<br />\n就唔應該用個「彌」字<br />\n因為佢根本就唔係讀尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017c880a3801d080e27ff0f6a77f12d65d0cffaf","tid":538811,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93586336b5b4e24ef22952d549cc5d75aa57120f","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88fc29ef2668132902da70566920f7145de45574","tid":538811,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"彌係一字多音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可讀微可讀尼<br />\n唔可以話尼唔係其中正確讀法，而依家普及黎講都係聽尼音多過微音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"其實多人讀尼都唔代表係正音<br />\n只不過大家都有共識接受呢個讀音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔係正音先<br />\n字典已經講左係有兩個音，一個原音另一個異讀音，你唔可能話讀尼係錯音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你果種概念係應用喺明顯讀錯，例如個冼字讀左做洗音，咁讀洗當然唔會係正音，冼先係唯一正音，另一個例子讀個鳩字，最正音就真係粗口果個音，但亦有人讀溝，屬於異讀類既一種正音，唔可以講係讀錯，應該係視為另一種選擇<br />\n<br />\n所以讀尼係無話錯唔錯，只係讀既人一個選擇"},{"pid":"84e2dfa97dc9e1d1aa63f2e0454826fff8474f3c","tid":538811,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"379d490cf816ac74ae20a9a2f9fe03ab709d2f71","tid":538811,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e751d81dead3e0f30a95bc5a0d7c7733928ac5a","tid":538811,"uid":143505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7faa57fa3bc257ffb15ae21dc6cbfdbed71292ea","tid":538811,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"同埋彌敦道讀尼敦係因為音譯nathan，呢個係外國傳音<br />\n咁你話讀尼敦近啲定微敦近呢<br />\n仲話你讀微敦唔會糾正人地尼敦<br />\n正常應該係人地讀尼敦去糾正你先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"咁如果係音譯<br />\n就唔應該用個「彌」字<br />\n因為佢根本就唔係讀尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"你要完全準似nathan就變左喱騰道<br />\n但彌敦當時係英國一啲有名望既人物黎<br />\n你覺得佢地英國人會鍾意用彌敦定喱騰先<br />\n因為英國係有一班人專改漢字名，所以先會用彌(尼)敦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d487a5e954ae29684424696b68bba02821bf30","tid":538811,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"殘體字都係約定俗成<br />\n<br />\n中國 + 馬來 + 新加坡 + 海外蝗 十幾億人約定俗成"}]}